          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>smashed cucumber</strong> (save the rest for later!) to a bowl with your <strong>yoghurt</strong>, <strong>mint sauce </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chunky tzatziki</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
