            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> halloumi</strong> with the <strong>buttery potatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped lettuce</strong> and <strong>chunky tzatziki</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the lettuce with the<strong> remaining smashed cucumber</strong>, then dress with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Drizzle your<strong> red chilli relish</strong> over the halloumi</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
